videos.headline: Howell connects with Brown for 62-yard UNC TD
videos.description: Sam Howell drops a dime to Dyami Brown who scores a 62-yard UNC touchdown to give the Tar Heels a 10-0 lead over Miami.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howell connects with Brown for 62-yard UNC TD) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris bursts through UNC defense for Miami TD
videos.description: Cam'Ron Harris takes the handoff and bulldozes his way four yards into the end zone to score a Hurricanes touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harris bursts through UNC defense for Miami TD) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Newsome dives to reel in UNC TD catch
videos.description: Sam Howell drops a dime to Dazz Newsome who dives to make the 10-yard UNC touchdown catch to retake the lead 28-25.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Newsome dives to reel in UNC TD catch) 2019/09/07 ESHEET
